@startuml
title Chain of Responsibility

skinparam legendBackgroundColor #f9f9f9
skinparam legendBorderColor #999999

legend right
**Intent**: Pass requests along a chain; let multiple objects try handling it.

**Use when**: Decouple sender from receiver; flexible routing.

**Key participants**: Handler, ConcreteHandler, chain links.
endlegend

abstract class Handler {
  -next : Handler
  +setNext(h: Handler) : Handler
  +handle(req: Request)
}

class ConcreteHandlerA
class ConcreteHandlerB

class Request

Handler <|-- ConcreteHandlerA
Handler <|-- ConcreteHandlerB
Handler o-- Handler : next
ConcreteHandlerA ..> Request
ConcreteHandlerB ..> Request
@enduml